{"tid":114934,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[一氣呵成] 一條腸去東京 失魂遊記+感想","createTime":"2017-02-10T07:35:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-10T10:02:03.000Z","uid":81951,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fef6ff8ee6749e0a2ef98c64cf8e0fcff89740bf","tid":114934,"uid":81951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T07:35:53.000Z","msg":"今次算係重新開一次舊post 因為之前個post比較亂亦開錯台 極速沉咗底 多謝幾位巴絲打喺上個post嘅支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n成個行程3日3夜<br />\n<br />\n2月6號 出發!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n晨咁早5:30起身 準備好出門口搭巴士 由屋企樓下到機場要搭一個鐘左右 班機8:40 <br />\n<br />\n第一日唔記得影相 凈得少少 失敗中嘅失敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到步第一樣就係買車飛同電話卡<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/10/152612_5be3d397ac25ad1d1a4faee9e82f92e3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F10%2F152612_5be3d397ac25ad1d1a4faee9e82f92e3.jpg&h=2bbe4e30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由羽田機場出發去東銀座站 要先搭京急線再轉淺草線 京急線要額外買飛 410 yen<br />\n<br />\n去到東銀座 死喇 張sim卡上唔到網<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  佢話PDP authentication failure 冇咗google map 淆晒底 好彩酒店算近地鐵站 搵咗20分鐘總算到咗<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我住嘅係Capsule形式嘅酒店<br />\n酒店門口<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/68v185s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F68v185s.jpg&h=441ee472&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n床位<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/10/153240_1d2b40d1377696524786744b1810b78d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F10%2F153240_1d2b40d1377696524786744b1810b78d.jpg&h=3bae3e4a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fhx4CbV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffhx4CbV.jpg&h=5bf55920&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由於冇乜點plan行程 決定鳩行吓<br />\n搭車去到東京站 見到我男神<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/573R99m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F573R99m.jpg&h=1e3e9f76&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/10/153541_ddb2cc5aa3b26c0b3125bd685fca1d9e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F10%2F153541_ddb2cc5aa3b26c0b3125bd685fca1d9e.jpg&h=818e5835&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/10/153541_b80e06b566b463fa9569192de6d45350.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F10%2F153541_b80e06b566b463fa9569192de6d45350.jpg&h=e77bf086&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ac62e486779ccb9bb41448510565c861cba0c322","tid":114934,"uid":12994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T07:37:35.000Z","msg":"嘩 呢啲點沖涼？<br />\n平好多？"},{"pid":"289ef13c44ef78c45d7cebeac6f1574efa0bb0ee","tid":114934,"uid":81951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T07:50:29.000Z","msg":"第一日晚求其搵間鋪頭食啲嘢就返酒店 早啲瞓因為第二朝係非常期待嘅行程 去壽司大食Omakase<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2月7號<br />\n朝早4:30起身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 徒步行去築地<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/km8rg37.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkm8rg37.jpg&h=c060a88e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c1WY6H0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc1WY6H0.jpg&h=b1977abf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t3Stun2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft3Stun2.jpg&h=5af9e000&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n排隊排到角落頭<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y63V7JR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY63V7JR.jpg&h=5e53a507&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/10/154142_0b28d99527049b990e7ec9673282e12f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F10%2F154142_0b28d99527049b990e7ec9673282e12f.jpg&h=7ce22fbc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n排咗成個鐘 終於排到門口<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y6530km.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy6530km.jpg&h=76328e0d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/10/154235_2bc4c393ac12ecb267a6f22ae1a44812.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F10%2F154235_2bc4c393ac12ecb267a6f22ae1a44812.jpg&h=68ca10d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n伙記攞熱茶出嚟俾大家飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/10/154416_167946bdb55512cd28a4e921f62bd5a6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F10%2F154416_167946bdb55512cd28a4e921f62bd5a6.jpg&h=bfd4c284&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n終於可以入去 排到震都腳埋<br />\n附上成個course 頭兩個唔記得影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/10/154646_63116d414a84013d1a8b5c9b50051957.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F10%2F154646_63116d414a84013d1a8b5c9b50051957.jpg&h=d7961900&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eWyF2mr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeWyF2mr.jpg&h=8178ae67&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dq65ccc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDq65ccc.jpg&h=c9bab8c3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/89x514a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F89x514a.jpg&h=de0bc134&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/10/154648_58a85a625d0a4a474e5da93586fc4596.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F10%2F154648_58a85a625d0a4a474e5da93586fc4596.jpg&h=bd1399a8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/10/154710_adac6b3b86595b4fe44f63908fcbc720.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F10%2F154710_adac6b3b86595b4fe44f63908fcbc720.jpg&h=dd84ff40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好邪惡<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/10/154739_bb40df2e8e5e09dd0eafb2058586be65.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F10%2F154739_bb40df2e8e5e09dd0eafb2058586be65.jpg&h=87dcd5bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/10/154806_dbc7f8276d9003d012a8de0d822b1ebc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F10%2F154806_dbc7f8276d9003d012a8de0d822b1ebc.jpg&h=edf01de8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aCbUFg3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaCbUFg3.jpg&h=294f6b07&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O50e8pk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO50e8pk.jpg&h=6b691869&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5g6PvA5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5g6PvA5.jpg&h=7572b345&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/34H0Kn1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F34H0Kn1.jpg&h=e0502d9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後係自選一樣 我揀咗呢樣<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/10/154852_5c76772a9a0162a3256b6f7f00a41f71.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F10%2F154852_5c76772a9a0162a3256b6f7f00a41f71.jpg&h=ac572266&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n到我食完走嘅時候 出面仲有好多人排緊 記住要早啲嚟排隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/40DA9xf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F40DA9xf.jpg&h=0d07b9fb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f17a4fc975b3d6b81be1a8076fd8fcb5c53a35cf","tid":114934,"uid":81951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T07:51:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>嘩 呢啲點沖涼？<br />\n平好多？</blockquote><br />\n佢有沖涼房同廁所"},{"pid":"f1bebf2cc980e23827110aa52ba9768fc3498702","tid":114934,"uid":81951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T07:53:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>嘩 呢啲點沖涼？<br />\n平好多？</blockquote><br />\n佢有沖涼房同廁所<br />\n3夜凈係125蚊澳紙<br />\n</blockquote>"},{"pid":"604655b0a7ae839e3b7011fc9c7e289324ce99c6","tid":114934,"uid":18908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T08:31:54.000Z","msg":"咁樣係Airbnb book民宿好過啦 <br />\n兩舊水一晚都大把選擇"},{"pid":"d4f573f1ff7b7275286613e5b0e1dcb5fa0d7981","tid":114934,"uid":81951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T08:56:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁樣係Airbnb book民宿好過啦 <br />\n兩舊水一晚都大把選擇</blockquote><br />\nbook嗰陣時唔知有airbnb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce869e2fff04dca30732dd19a6074dc59677f0d5","tid":114934,"uid":81951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T09:06:34.000Z","msg":"之後去咗赤羽橋望下東京鐵塔<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wx00646.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwx00646.jpg&h=533a46f7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/10/165703_fcfe919f946e9a1e063bc3d1c4b13ea2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F10%2F165703_fcfe919f946e9a1e063bc3d1c4b13ea2.jpg&h=01c5c24d&s={SIZE}\" /